TopicTitle: What goes "Vroom Vroom" and has wheels?

Articles.Content:
Seriously, I don't know. Someone asked this to me when I was 2 and haven't been able to figure it out.

I've thought it might be one of these

But I don't know. This one doesn't really make any sound at all. Please help, if you know what it is, download this craft here: https://www.dropbox.com/s/uspo3brl636gxh1/Car.craft?dl=0

Or if you want to support me (not necessarily donate) go here (to download it) https://sites.google.com/site/gimbalscrafts/craft-repository/subassemblies

NOTE: IT IS A SUBASSEMBLY. IT GOES IN THE SUBASSEMBLY FOLDER. OR ELSE IT WON'T WORK.

Oh wait, here's some craft specs:

============================================

Top speed: 25 m/s

Crew capaccity: 4K*

Mass: not sure, but if you haven't exploded it's less than 17 tonnes

File Size: 44K**

Cool Level: Something good to have around... I guess...

Body Color: White, Gray.

*K as in Kerbals

**K not for kerbals
